    "That is, instead of targeting an individual instance, performance is averaged over the entire population.",
    "MCDA is more than just predictions based on examples.",
    "Its aim is to analyze the decision-making context by identifying the problem with its actors, potential alternatives and their consequences, and the stakes.",
    "The actors are stakeholders concerned by the decision.",
    "Their points of view are expressed through evaluation criteria."
